# Intuit Design System - Space Token Library

## Primitive Space Tokens (DO NOT USE DIRECTLY IN PLUGINS)

- `--space-0`: 0
- `--space-2`: 2px
- `--space-4`: 4px
- `--space-6`: 6px
- `--space-8`: 8px
- `--space-10`: 10px
- `--space-12`: 12px
- `--space-16`: 16px
- `--space-20`: 20px
- `--space-24`: 24px
- `--space-32`: 32px
- `--space-40`: 40px
- `--space-56`: 56px
- `--space-60`: 60px
- `--space-72`: 72px
- `--space-96`: 96px

## Semantic Space Tokens (USE THESE IN PLUGINS)

### Column
- `--space-column-gap-large`: --space-24 /* Large space used between columns of a grid or collection of components. */
- `--space-column-gap-medium`: --space-20 /* Default space used between columns of a grid or collection of components. */
- `--space-column-gap-small`: --space-16 /* Small space used between columns of a grid or collection of components. */
- `--space-column-gap-x-large`: --space-40 /* Largest space used between columns of a grid or collection of components. */
- `--space-column-gap-x-small`: --space-8 /* Smallest space used between columns of a grid or collection of components. */
- `--space-column-gap-xx-small`: --space-4 /* Extra Smallest space used between columns of a grid or collection of components. */

### Component
- `--space-component-gap-large`: --space-12 /* Gaps between text or icon elements */
- `--space-component-gap-medium`: --space-8 /* Gaps between text or icon elements */
- `--space-component-gap-small`: --space-4 /* Gaps between text or icon elements */
- `--space-component-gap-x-small`: --space-2 /* Gaps between text or icon elements */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-large`: --space-10 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-medium`: --space-8 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-small`: --space-6 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-x-large`: --space-12 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-x-small`: --space-4 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-xx-large`: --space-16 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-xx-small`: --space-2 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-xxx-large`: --space-20 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-inline-padding-xxx-small`: --space-0 /* Horizontal padding */
- `--space-component-stack-padding-large`: --space-8 /* Vertical padding */
- `--space-component-stack-padding-medium`: --space-6 /* Vertical padding */
- `--space-component-stack-padding-small`: --space-4 /* Vertical padding */
- `--space-component-stack-padding-x-large`: --space-10 /* Vertical padding */
- `--space-component-stack-padding-x-small`: --space-2 /* Vertical padding */
- `--space-component-stack-padding-xx-small`: --space-0 /* Vertical padding */

### Container
- `--space-container-padding-large`: --space-24 /* Large container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-medium`: --space-20 /* Medium container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-small`: --space-16 /* Small container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-x-large`: --space-32 /* Extra large container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-x-small`: --space-12 /* Extra small container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-xx-large`: --space-40 /* Extra extra large container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-xx-small`: --space-8 /* Extra extra small container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-xxx-large`: --space-60 /* Extra extra extra large container padding (any direction). */
- `--space-container-padding-xxx-small`: --space-4 /* Extra extra extra small container padding (any direction). */

### Input
- `--space-input-inline-padding-medium`: --space-8 /* For the left and right padding of medium input fields */
- `--space-input-inline-padding-small`: --space-8 /* For the left and right padding of small input fields */
- `--space-input-stack-padding-medium`: --space-8 /* For the top and bottom padding of medium input fields */
- `--space-input-stack-padding-small`: --space-6 /* For the top and bottom padding of small input fields */

### Large
- `--space-large`: --space-24 /* Large size of optional, theme-specific scale of spacing tokens for general purpose use. */

### Medium
- `--space-medium`: --space-16 /* Medium size of optional, theme-specific scale of spacing tokens for general purpose use. */

### Page
- `--space-page-inline`: --space-20 /* Margin of the main page content */

### Row
- `--space-row-gap-large`: --space-40 /* Large space used between rows of a page layout or collection of components. */
- `--space-row-gap-medium`: --space-20 /* Default (Medium) space used between rows of a page layout or collection of components. */
- `--space-row-gap-small`: --space-12 /* Small space used between rows of a page layout or collection of components. */
- `--space-row-gap-x-large`: --space-60 /* Largest space used between rows of a page layout or collection of components. */
- `--space-row-gap-x-small`: --space-8 /* Smallest space used between rows of a page layout or collection of components. */

### Small
- `--space-small`: --space-12 /* Small size of optional, theme-specific scale of spacing tokens for general purpose use. */

### X
- `--space-x-large`: --space-40 /* Optional, theme-specific scale of spacing tokens for general purpose use. */
- `--space-x-small`: --space-8 /* Optional, theme-specific scale of spacing tokens for general purpose use. */
